                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/3287" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-0791</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9630 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">点滴关怀：如何让职场更有爱</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">无</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">葛建华</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国政法大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">点滴关怀</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">精益创业；平台经济；O2O；共享经济；弹性福利；顾客价值；场景营销；2018百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> Lean startup; O2O; Platform Economics; Shared economy; Flexible benefits; Customer value; Scene marketing</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新创企业如何选择市场切入点并持续推进？客户价值和企业价值如何完美结合？企业的商业模式如何在竞争中逐步完善？……这些问题贯穿于点滴关怀发展的全过程，促使其在市场考验中获得快速成长。2015年6月上线以来，点滴关怀面向不同企业提供个性化福利解决方案，围绕企业员工服务提供多种线上线下的增值服务和定制模块，帮助企业提高员工的归属感……在这个过程中，企业商业模式经历了从1.0到4.0的变化，企业愿景逐步实现：成为互联网+员工服务领域的第一品牌，服务于企业福利绩效改善、提升员工满意度及幸福感，让职场更有爱。案例凸显了蔡虎作为创业者对市场趋势和技术发展的敏锐把握及融合能力，凸显了创业团队强大的产品开发能力和产品市场化的运营能力，也凸显了平台经济所具有的开放共享、合作共赢的特征。通过此案例，读者可更多地了解互联网创业特点和创业团队特质。这些成就，凸显了蔡虎作为创业者对市场趋势和技术发展的敏锐把握及融合能力，以及联合同行共同构建“互联网+员工服务”平台实现合作共赢的发展理念，也凸显了互联网本身所具有的开放共享特征。通过此案例，读者可更好地了解互联网创业特点和创业者特质。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Abstrac: How to choose the market entry point and keep pushing forward?How to integrate customer value and firm value perfectly? How to improve the business model gradually in the market competition? ...... These problems run through the whole process of the development of ddguanhuai, which promote its rapid growth in fierce competition. Since June 2015, for different business customers, ddguanhuai has provided them personalized welfare solution plans, and a variety of on-line and off-line value-added services and customized modules for their staffs, all of which contributed to enhance their staff&#39;s sense of belonging... In this process, the business model of ddguanhuai has experienced the change from Version 1.0 to 4.0, and its vision——becoming the first brand in the field of Internet + staff service, serving the companies’ welfare improvement, improving employee’s satisfaction and happiness, and providing more love in the workplace——has gradually implemented.
This Case study highlights that, as ddguanhuai’s founder, Mr. Hu Cai has sharp insight into market trends and technology development, together with integration abilities. It also highlights the strong capabilities for product development and marketing of its venture team, and the characteristics of open sharing and win-win cooperation of the platform&#39;s economy. Through this case study, readers will have a better understanding about the characteristics of Internet business startups and entrepreneurs.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2018</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《精益创业》、《平台经济》、《商业模式》、《顾客价值》、《场景营销》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">精益创业、平台经济、商业模式</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2018-07</td>
